Description: Sparebank 1 Ringerike Hadeland is a Norway-based savings bank. The Bank offers a broad range of banking and investment products to retail and corporate customers. The services include daily banking activities, bor-rowing, personal insurance, non-life insurance and savings operations, online and mobile banking services, card issue, payment services, mortgage and different kind of small loans, saving and retire account and real estate credit among others.
